about.summary: Expat XML parser library in C

name: expat
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "2.1.0" %}

package:
    name: expat
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: expat-{{ version }}.tar.bz2
    url: http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/expat/expat/{{ version }}/expat-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    md5: dd7dab7a5fea97d2a6a43f511449b7cd

build:
    number: 2
    features:
        - vc9  # [win and py27]
        - vc10  # [win and py34]
        - vc14  # [win and py35]

requirements:
    build:
        - cmake  # [win]
        - python  # [win]
        - msinttypes  # [win]

test:
    requires:
        - python {{ environ['PY_VER'] + '*' }}  # [win]
    commands:
        - xmlwf -h

about:
    home: http://expat.sourceforge.net/
    license: MIT
    summary: Expat XML parser library in C

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - kwilcox
        - ocefpaf
        - pelson
